# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok middlesbrough manager and england assistant coach steve mcclaren can leave if he is asked to be the successor to england coach sven-goran eriksson his club chairman said on sunday .
# ::alignments
(p / possible-01
      :ARG1 (l / leave-11
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Steve"
                        :op2 "McCcclaren")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (t / team
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Middlesbrough"))
                        :ARG3 (m / manage-01))
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (t2 / team
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "England"))
                        :ARG3 (c / coach
                              :ARG0-of (a / assist-01))))
            :condition (a2 / ask-02
                  :ARG1 (s / succeed-02
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Sven-goran"
                                    :op2 "Eriksson")
                              :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 t2
                                    :ARG2 (c2 / chairman))))
                  :ARG2 p2)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))))

                              :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                    :ARG1-of (w / worth-01

                                                :op2 (a5 / appliance)
                                                :op3 (f2 / furniture)))))

                              :ARG0 p

                                          :mod (c3 / credit)))
                              :ARG1-of (p2 / permit-01
                                    :polarity -))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (f3 / friday))))

# ::alignments
(c / condemn-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG1-of (n / neighbor-01
                  :ARG2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Fiji"))))
      :ARG1 (d / decide-01
            :ARG0 (r / regime
                  :mod (m / military))
            :ARG0-of (f / force-01
                  :ARG1 (c2 / corporation
                        :mod (n3 / news)
                        :poss (p3 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Rupert"
                                    :op2 "Murdoch")))
                  :ARG2 (o / or
                        :op1 (s / sell-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG1 (n5 / newspaper
                                    :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (l / large)
                                          :ARG3 (m2 / most)
                                          :ARG5 (n6 / newspaper
                                                :location (n7 / nation
                                                      :mod (p4 / pacific))))
                                    :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (o2 / old)
                                          :ARG3 (m3 / most)
                                          :ARG5 n6)))
                        :op2 (c3 / close-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG1 n5))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))
